  "remarks": "A leader of an armed group linked to Al-Nusrah Front for the People of\nthe Levant (QDe.137) and a key facilitator for a Syrian foreign terrorist fighter\nnetwork. Active in terrorist propaganda through the Internet. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 2368 (2017) was concluded on 4 Dec. 2019. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 2610 (2021) was concluded on 30 October 2023.  INTERPOL-UN Security Council Special Notice web link:https://www.interpol.int/en/How-we-work/Notices/View-UN-Notices-Individuals",
